      <title>摩根士丹利和匯豐銀行因中國交易放緩而削減亞洲投資銀行職位</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/morgan-stanley-cut-around-50-investment-banking-jobs-asia-pacific-sources-say-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[消息人士稱，摩根士丹利和匯豐銀行本週將在亞太地區裁員數十個投資銀行職位，因為它們加大了成本削減力度，而中國和香港的交易疲軟以及市場低迷給商業前景帶來了壓力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/morgan-stanley-cut-around-50-investment-banking-jobs-asia-pacific-sources-say-2024-04-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 02:58:15 GMT</pubDate>
